{"title":"QQ浏览器 | PC版的AI进化","slug":"rsarh9r77xdh0lzi","summary":"30年过去了，浏览器类产品在AI技术的狂飙突进下，终迎来新生。已诞生15年的QQ浏览器PC版，在今年也迎来了它的AI升级，在「浏览器+AI插件」和「AI原生浏览器」并行的当下，也探索了让AI“智感”在用户体验旅程中全方位的融入。 一、框架：简洁有序的AI“智感”基座 AI的能力在","category":"2. 国内产品","tags":["PART6️⃣ AI产品设计案例分析库","2. 国内产品"],"featured":false,"order":92,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2026-01-05","wordCount":3362,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/rsarh9r77xdh0lzi","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"u5dff63df\" id=\"u5dff63df\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9a6aadc0\" id=\"u9a6aadc0\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">30年过去了，浏览器类产品在AI技术的狂飙突进下，终迎来新生。已诞生15年的QQ浏览器PC版，在今年也迎来了它的AI升级，在「浏览器+AI插件」和「AI原生浏览器」并行的当下，也探索了让AI“智感”在用户体验旅程中全方位的融入。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"e4757560\" id=\"e4757560\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8a546188\" id=\"u8a546188\" class=\"lake-fontsize-18\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">一、框架：简洁有序的AI“智感”基座</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ub42455ab\" id=\"ub42455ab\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3ca75e87\" id=\"u3ca75e87\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">AI的能力在不断演化着，浏览框架作为体验的基座，需要根据技术发展的大趋势，尽可能稳定而超前地进行演变，才能</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u355f66b0\" id=\"u355f66b0\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">让用户在面对AI的“灵动”时，仍感到稳定与可控</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2d922ecb\" id=\"u2d922ecb\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2f1a3527\" id=\"u2f1a3527\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6d015074\" id=\"u6d015074\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在PC上，浏览器是集合了用户与信息全方位交互（获取、消费、处理、创造等）的产品，洞察AI带来的人与信息交互方式变化的大趋势，才能构建好简洁有序的“智感”基座。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"57e019c9\" id=\"57e019c9\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0cd6859a\" id=\"u0cd6859a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.1 AI深刻改变人与信息的关系，也影响着基座体验演进方向</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uc7e2cb6a\" id=\"uc7e2cb6a\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620814679-fe8f7a2c-78da-4b96-b1d0-c20270a3e0f2.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22udf2b154c-e615-4f40-8eed-6c480d28240%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f0f5f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub166db43%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"feaa1566\" id=\"feaa1566\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b566406\" id=\"u5b566406\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.2 更简洁：提升信噪比，为AI搭好台</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u17ad2937\" id=\"u17ad2937\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u89c100ef\" id=\"u89c100ef\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">以前没有大模型参与理解网页，各类网页浏览工具只能上架陈列出来，才能让用户发现并根据需要去使用。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6dd536b1\" id=\"u6dd536b1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7b845997\" id=\"u7b845997\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">有了AI大模型的加持，让好的功能在需要时会被推送给用户，不依赖一直外露。这使我们敢于对原有的功能入口</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u50277c97\" id=\"u50277c97\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">收折、合并、简化</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud84909e1\" id=\"ud84909e1\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">，而不用担心用户找不到。</span><span data-lake-id=\"u46e2edba\" id=\"u46e2edba\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"babd8a48\" id=\"babd8a48\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8c512c50\" id=\"u8c512c50\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.2.1 做减法，框架上外露的固定入口持续精简</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u64cf69c1\" id=\"u64cf69c1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2e33847d\" id=\"u2e33847d\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">地址栏右侧的功能入口，进行了多轮的简化收折，最新版固定入口已精简到4个，识别场景需求后，功能会适时出现。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uca69e8b8\" id=\"uca69e8b8\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620814679-4d8e742a-38d7-4825-b999-2150e23f3058.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u5e5b0ddd-978f-4c58-a6c2-be397293eea%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%237d7c79%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub49c141c%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"ee7d522e\" id=\"ee7d522e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubffeb7ad\" id=\"ubffeb7ad\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.2.2 做合并，找功能更简单</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u70ecfcf9\" id=\"u70ecfcf9\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9f048721\" id=\"u9f048721\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">原本分散在三个入口中的菜单、个人中心、应用中心，全部合一，更为合理的分区定义后，找功能效率更高。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0efa2532\" id=\"u0efa2532\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620814694-901a0f64-9736-49fd-b0fa-515ffaba10c7.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u798fc9fd-be68-47fc-b642-122eea2c9c0%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%235d5c5c%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u15f66db0%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"42bae351\" id=\"42bae351\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u45ac2070\" id=\"u45ac2070\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.2.3 调主次，更聚焦当前网页</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u26c02fcf\" id=\"u26c02fcf\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u01a42467\" id=\"u01a42467\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">AI会使得用户在当前网页就能完成更多任务，反复切换会减少，三行框架整体高度不变的情况下，加大网页工具栏高度，更聚焦，点击区更大，使用更舒适。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u11f8e581\" id=\"u11f8e581\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1767620814724-90596f30-e6c7-4905-a99c-b05d3a056a47.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u1811d215-409b-4cd5-b88c-fb344ecbf4b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A607%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e8eff7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u19756066%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"11767170\" id=\"11767170\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7a083216\" id=\"u7a083216\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.3 更多变：使信息能在多类框架中任意穿行</span></strong></h2><h3 data-lake-id=\"9b9d391d\" id=\"9b9d391d\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7c2c9852\" id=\"u7c2c9852\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.3.1 灵活的容器，信息可以任意框架展示并互相转换</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uc0b34451\" id=\"uc0b34451\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ude067196\" id=\"ude067196\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">原本以一个个标签页为基础单元的信息处理行为，有可能因为AI的辅助，变成流式：一些信息可能带着任务，需要与不同的页面、甚至其他系统应用发生交替、伴随等关系，</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua5443979\" id=\"ua5443979\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">创造多变的信息容器定义</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8b6cd19c\" id=\"u8b6cd19c\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">，使信息在其间的穿行能实现，更有序，且易于理解。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3e44bdf1\" id=\"u3e44bdf1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620814794-e0264c9e-1443-4d9d-8898-2d15f274cc03.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u78b11dc0-01ab-4043-8c72-37bfb3989a4%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%232c2c2c%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uaa2323a3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"9d3c5609\" id=\"9d3c5609\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2d16f2e1\" id=\"u2d16f2e1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.3.2 减少框架层级，降低多变带来的负担</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u77723ade\" id=\"u77723ade\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue4fd7780\" id=\"ue4fd7780\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">轻量化框架，运用多种设计手法做页面分区，简化框架层级，改善了旧版本竖版工作台打开、</span><span data-lake-id=\"u666a4ea0\" id=\"u666a4ea0\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">侧边栏打开、分屏多层框套框的复杂、厚重样式。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf216cb89\" id=\"uf216cb89\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620815242-0bcd07f1-008a-49e9-a182-0fa9053c6390.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ubcf0112b-a007-46ec-bc59-0172ce68dad%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23eaf2fb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2228cb93%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc036f22f\" id=\"uc036f22f\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1767620815286-f7f25ac3-aa37-4773-af29-1ede8d217d29.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ude32ee8a-72bc-4644-873a-c174afed108%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A607%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2389dba1%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ud7b49506%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"eb04d1a8\" id=\"eb04d1a8\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf4c25726\" id=\"uf4c25726\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.4 更畅通：数据资产的规整能促进流动</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"ub529360e\" id=\"ub529360e\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3a402422\" id=\"u3a402422\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">十多年累计下的用户资产类型多样，书签类型就有三种，将其合并规整，后续AI才有机会提供更有价值的服务。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5532da7c\" id=\"u5532da7c\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620815240-a16e5ccb-11cc-483e-910c-eda66c612c97.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub8e77c47-ad0e-4c10-83bf-fefe49185fb%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23a9a89e%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ufaa4d83a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"2fa8fe43\" id=\"2fa8fe43\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u05918d06\" id=\"u05918d06\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.5 表达演化：从“待命”到“参与”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u0099dfb0\" id=\"u0099dfb0\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uba35fb09\" id=\"uba35fb09\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">UI表达从“待命”到“参与”，是AI在框架上的集中体现。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u30e1a713\" id=\"u30e1a713\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">通过“光影逻辑”的提出，定义智能的可视化韵律</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u826dc818\" id=\"u826dc818\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc5bd4add\" id=\"uc5bd4add\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3232c7d3\" id=\"u3232c7d3\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">本次AI升级中，</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue5a99e04\" id=\"ue5a99e04\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">定义了一套与AI工作流同构的视觉语法</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u68b694ea\" id=\"u68b694ea\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">：“聚光”=意图聚焦，“流光”=思考过程，“溢光”=能力就绪，这一套视觉语法的定义，符合用户的自然认知，让AI的灵动有了稳定的输出形态，建立了用户对AI工作流的认知基础。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u64139437\" id=\"u64139437\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1767620815302-8f927314-a3a8-4c05-bcac-ec614223b05c.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ue9315b1a-f8ed-440b-a775-f9202400532%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A607%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23191919%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u71fe1e94%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u94f53cf3\" id=\"u94f53cf3\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub9b2c7a0\" id=\"ub9b2c7a0\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">下面我们可以从实例中看看这套AI视觉语法的运用。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8dff6f51\" id=\"u8dff6f51\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u547dbe11\" id=\"u547dbe11\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">框架的 AI+ 功能入口，就是通过“聚光”=意图聚焦，“溢光”=能力就绪的视觉语法，来完成不同场景下功能的推送，以及能力准备就绪的表达。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1f3717c8\" id=\"u1f3717c8\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1767620815821-7515fe37-e603-4606-854e-4b046c25b501.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc745b042-46cc-4c8f-860a-561e9b7e8d8%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A607%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f6f8fd%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ud44d0209%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u85acee1a\" id=\"u85acee1a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u906a0d7d\" id=\"u906a0d7d\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">用AI协助整理标签页的分组，对用户来说不是一个常用的功能，过程中，标签页整理能力的准备就绪，整理进行中，和完成后的操作聚焦，就是通过溢光、流光、聚光的过程反馈，将标签整理的工作流程具象化。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"udfaf103e\" id=\"udfaf103e\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1767620815788-9546ebe6-56f2-47f5-989a-cd46db52581d.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud73e7aa5-8439-4050-a6b2-8708e0946ee%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A607%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23eaf9ee%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue155ea88%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"dd37fe11\" id=\"dd37fe11\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0f9b6cd2\" id=\"u0f9b6cd2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-18\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">二、AI 旅程：全场景感知的“智感”体验</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ufeb69739\" id=\"ufeb69739\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u49618394\" id=\"u49618394\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">“智感”不是一套僵化的交互模版，而是一种能够随需而变的流体体验。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5dd15e20\" id=\"u5dd15e20\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ube68cf65\" id=\"ube68cf65\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">面对浏览器中复杂的消费形态，我们拒绝了“一刀切”的侧边栏设计，而是根据用户所处的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4c0fce82\" id=\"u4c0fce82\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">阅读、聆听、观看、代办</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc6a74838\" id=\"uc6a74838\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">四个核心场景，定制了四种截然不同的“智感”表达，让体验在不同感官维度下都能精准落地。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"7290c4ca\" id=\"7290c4ca\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2ef42d8b\" id=\"u2ef42d8b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.1 网页阅读：信息提纯的“结构之美”</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u2b6e7a75\" id=\"u2b6e7a75\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7debfbd4\" id=\"u7debfbd4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">适用功能：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2b5b97cd\" id=\"u2b5b97cd\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">AI 总结、AI 思维导图、AI文件总结、 AI资源嗅探</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"uef3377f1\" id=\"uef3377f1\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u46d0b841\" id=\"u46d0b841\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">在最基础的图文阅读场景中，“智感”并非改变阅读的内容，而是通过 AI 的介入，让原本厚重、杂乱的网页回归</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6d8d2bc1\" id=\"u6d8d2bc1\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">结构的清澈、信息的单纯</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u50ccf5aa\" id=\"u50ccf5aa\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"9ce4e67f\" id=\"9ce4e67f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u76724c91\" id=\"u76724c91\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.1.1 因需而变的“形态重组”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"ub63e773a\" id=\"ub63e773a\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc50cdd52\" id=\"uc50cdd52\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">为了让信息以最适合被吸收的结构呈现，我们在统一的智能容器下设计了不同的结果形态。AI 不再是单一的文本输出：需要网页总结，它输出结构清晰的流式文本 ；需要主线脉络，它直接渲染为可交互的思维导图组件；需要的是网页中的附件材料，它给出文中涉及的富媒体文件 。这种形态上的重塑，让用户能一眼看透信息的本质。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2e261381\" id=\"u2e261381\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620815792-69d1720f-6f02-4607-ad83-9cb496b8fec4.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u009926ef-c77b-4c5a-a78f-c823bdc02d8%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e6dcd7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u29647caf%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"b2e66a16\" id=\"b2e66a16\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u72dc0904\" id=\"u72dc0904\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.1.2 多维并行的“空间结构”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u24459a07\" id=\"u24459a07\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaa6eaf76\" id=\"uaa6eaf76\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">针对传统 AI 对话“线性流”导致的历史内容（如总结、脑图）容易被淹没、难以回溯定位的痛点，我们沿用了浏览器用户最熟悉的“新建标签页”习惯。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uca4354f1\" id=\"uca4354f1\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">用户不再需要在长长的对话记录中反复滑动寻找，而是可以像新建网页标签一样，独立开启多个 AI 功能窗口。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubdc56237\" id=\"ubdc56237\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">这种标签式的切换与对比，不仅符合浏览器的原生操作直觉，更让多源信息的对照查看变得轻而易举。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uefe6e741\" id=\"uefe6e741\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620816260-41f573ae-50b4-4aae-b1ad-c2ac312241f3.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6d337730-43be-4b3f-9842-65abbf306af%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23656565%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uacb45a68%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"d137111a\" id=\"d137111a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue821ae93\" id=\"ue821ae93\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.1.3 有据可依的“逻辑锚点”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u81b651c4\" id=\"u81b651c4\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3f0fb224\" id=\"u3f0fb224\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">为了建立阅读的信任感，我们在生成的内容中引入了“锚点与溯源”机制 。每一个 AI 生成的结论，都通过锚点提示用户上下文语境，并支持点击跳转 。这种结构化的引用设计，将 AI 的概括与原文的细节紧密挂钩，确保了信息的真实可查。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u521242b8\" id=\"u521242b8\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620816323-c7dbd0a9-5e80-4794-af2d-22b04607abd8.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9f9611c2-6bd1-4be1-9fa4-7c58f72ab8f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23d8d7cc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uca3dccbf%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"0f7c5e48\" id=\"0f7c5e48\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u90bbbd69\" id=\"u90bbbd69\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.2 沉浸聆听：语境感知的“声画共鸣”</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ufc9e5083\" id=\"ufc9e5083\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue61c0756\" id=\"ue61c0756\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">适用场景：</span><span data-lake-id=\"u0b096b88\" id=\"u0b096b88\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\"> </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u520a62be\" id=\"u520a62be\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">AI 听</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u786137e9\" id=\"u786137e9\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc06af4c\" id=\"ufc06af4c\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">当用户从“看”切换到“听”，“智感”便从理性的逻辑分析，转变为感性的生命律动。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"b68275f2\" id=\"b68275f2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8944cc1b\" id=\"u8944cc1b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.2.1 因地制宜的“语境定义”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u3457ddb9\" id=\"u3457ddb9\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u770b4ca2\" id=\"u770b4ca2\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">AI 听具备“页面类型感知”能力：识别到深度文章时，自动锚定为“播客模式”；识别到新闻资讯时，切换为“原文朗读”。在浏览网页时，它还会通过运营态气泡主动提示“可开启听模式”，在最合适的语境下提供服务。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud7abc628\" id=\"ud7abc628\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620816360-4220a19a-4d1e-4ad8-99d6-2f250da11f29.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u8bcb90ab-661d-4e10-9286-f77f2b470e8%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e0e0de%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue757403f%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"eca453cb\" id=\"eca453cb\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc51e0a2d\" id=\"uc51e0a2d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.2.2 零等待的“即时心流”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u4962bc72\" id=\"u4962bc72\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf039b50c\" id=\"uf039b50c\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">听觉体验不应是盲目的等待。我们通过“流式生成”技术实现了点击即听的零延迟，打破了传统播客的加载焦虑。同时，为了让声音“看得见”，我设计了和品牌同质感的气泡动效，色彩的呼吸动效让音频更有温度。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"d825bc99\" id=\"d825bc99\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue99db7ed\" id=\"ue99db7ed\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.3 视频消费：深度重构的“垂直洞察”</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u16891d37\" id=\"u16891d37\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc46cdfc2\" id=\"uc46cdfc2\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">适用功能：</span><span data-lake-id=\"u6c44a886\" id=\"u6c44a886\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\"> </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8b2bd924\" id=\"u8b2bd924\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">AI实时字幕、 AI视频助理</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u30c1237c\" id=\"u30c1237c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf3b6bd6e\" id=\"uf3b6bd6e\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">视频场景最大的痛点在于信息的封闭性。AI 的智感体现在它能打破播放器的物理外壳，通过局部锚定与整体重塑，帮助用户从“看热闹”变为“懂门道”的深度消费。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"3ef3e730\" id=\"3ef3e730\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u226c714f\" id=\"u226c714f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.3.1 局部维度的“精准锚定”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u74b7b547\" id=\"u74b7b547\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u65e45092\" id=\"u65e45092\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">让字幕成为比进度条更精确的“时间路标”。 AI 将字幕容器重构为视频的上下文索引。用户不仅能看到当前的台词，更能通过拖拽容器查看前后的语境关联。更重要的是，每一句字幕都是一个可点击的锚点，点击即可瞬间跳转到该句话的播放节点。这种“所见即所得”的跳转交互，比传统的拖拽进度条更加精准、从容。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"0ef97d6a\" id=\"0ef97d6a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uceb28151\" id=\"uceb28151\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.3.2 整体维度的“全景重塑”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u13ce66db\" id=\"u13ce66db\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u885d0796\" id=\"u885d0796\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">让视频变成一本有目录、有总结的“书”。 为了让用户快速吃透长视频，AI 视频助理从宏观视角对内容进行了逻辑重组。它能智能识别视频的情景段落，自动生成“可视化目录”与“分段总结”。用户不再需要从头看到尾，而是能通过目录俯瞰全篇脉络，快速定位感兴趣的章节。这种宏观视角的结构化重塑，彻底改变了线性观看的盲目，让视频消费拥有了阅读书籍般的清晰与深度。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"8a39abd4\" id=\"8a39abd4\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u34833a24\" id=\"u34833a24\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.4 任务代办：思维可视的“白盒执行”</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ue91e917a\" id=\"ue91e917a\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue7ca3c38\" id=\"ue7ca3c38\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">适用功能：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u12d563b2\" id=\"u12d563b2\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">AI下载助理、 AI更新助理、 AI订阅助理</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u69c69b4f\" id=\"u69c69b4f\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub80b34f7\" id=\"ub80b34f7\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">当用户需要 AI 去“找资源”或“办事情”时，场景从内容消费转向了任务代办。当 AI 替用户办事时，最大的阻碍是信任。我们通过“思维可视”的设计，把控制权交还给用户。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"e29c7070\" id=\"e29c7070\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uef655393\" id=\"uef655393\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.4.1 意图的“校准可视化”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u6045215b\" id=\"u6045215b\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u132244a9\" id=\"u132244a9\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">我们将 AI 隐性的思维校准过程，显性化为两个可见的阶段：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uee5285d3\" id=\"uee5285d3\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucfe8c478\" id=\"ucfe8c478\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">- 意图澄清</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u49aabb75\" id=\"u49aabb75\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"u9c7bdfc4\" id=\"u9c7bdfc4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">： 面对不确定或模糊的指令，AI 不会靠猜来执行，而是将疑惑外化为对话询问。针对复杂需求，它更能进行多轮询问，抽丝剥茧地将模糊的想法收敛为精准的目标（如：“您是指下载电影还是小说？”）。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0bc44440\" id=\"u0bc44440\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0ba8268a\" id=\"u0ba8268a\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">- 策略对齐</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u660f291c\" id=\"u660f291c\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"ue2ce45d9\" id=\"ue2ce45d9\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">： 目标明确后，AI 拒绝黑盒作业，而是主动进行计划策略的展示。在正式执行前，它会把“准备怎么干”（如：订阅的计划、监控的策略）铺陈在用户面前，确认策略无误后才开始运转。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u07eac2aa\" id=\"u07eac2aa\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620817115-5c9ed72a-f167-4ee0-b1d8-4e23b0c4664e.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ubefaf216-3ac4-4824-964d-0ab74034568%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e9e0d2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ud0ca9e1a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"b7d4d469\" id=\"b7d4d469\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u973b094d\" id=\"u973b094d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.4.2 路径的“推演可视化”</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u20f5fb4c\" id=\"u20f5fb4c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uec2c1a69\" id=\"uec2c1a69\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">我们拒绝给用户一个简单的进度条。我们将</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud4052dd8\" id=\"ud4052dd8\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\"> </span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uac26e4a2\" id=\"uac26e4a2\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">AI 拆解任务、检索信息、筛选决策</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufabd4456\" id=\"ufabd4456\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">的完整思维路径实时渲染在屏幕上。用户能眼见 AI 如何一步步逼近答案（如：正在搜索关键词 -&gt; 提取筛选数据 -&gt; 浏览网页）。这种动态的逻辑白盒，让用户像看着透明钟表运转一样，获得对智能代办的深度掌控。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub6ce4275\" id=\"ub6ce4275\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1767620816996-02b21f45-f0a5-49d3-a621-01d3221ca1fe.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u78a132a7-d4e5-4921-9c1b-82b8b57144d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4a0b2722-f7ee-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23eeeae0%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u0dfee07a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"eb2f055c\" id=\"eb2f055c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1b699c7e\" id=\"u1b699c7e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-18\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">三、下一代浏览器，不仅仅是“浏览”</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u0c10d62b\" id=\"u0c10d62b\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u27f28c62\" id=\"u27f28c62\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">所以，下一代浏览器的体验是什么？回顾QQ浏览器这款15年产品的升级，我们的答案是：智感。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucc365b2e\" id=\"ucc365b2e\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc3d0e9c9\" id=\"uc3d0e9c9\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">这次浏览器的升级不仅仅是一次功能的简化与叠加，更是一次对体验边界的拓宽。我们希望用“智感”来建立起浏览体验的标尺：在信息过载的时代做减法，让逻辑回归清晰；在冰冷的工具上做加法，让功能更有温度。这条“智感”之路才刚刚起航，我们将一起越走越远。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua258d9b4\" id=\"ua258d9b4\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9b07133b\" id=\"u9b07133b\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">​</span><br></p><blockquote data-lake-id=\"udb4bf0c9\" id=\"udb4bf0c9\"><p data-lake-id=\"u643fcc16\" id=\"u643fcc16\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u42c2bd41\" id=\"u42c2bd41\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/F9z-M7SOxRZnBL85OajSYw\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ue581370e\" id=\"ue581370e\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf5859df4\" id=\"uf5859df4\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/F9z-M7SOxRZnBL85OajSYw</span></a></p></blockquote>"}
